=\'text-align:justify\'><span lang=EN style=\'color:navy\'><span\r\nlang=EN style=\'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\";color:navy;\r\nfont-weight:normal\'>To get certified as ISO 9001:2008 compliant Flexicode underwent an evaluation process that included quality management system \r\n\r\ndevelopment, a management system documentation review, pre-audit, initial assessment, and clearance of non-conformances, all of which work towards \r\n\r\nidentifying corrective actions that eliminates non-conformance to the quality management standard.  The process culminated in a comprehensive registration \r\n\r\naudit by SAI. After correction and closure of all non-conformances, Flexicode received its ISO 9001:2008 certificate of registration on <strong>11th November \r\n\r\n2011.</strong>  The certification of compliance with ISO 9001:2008 recognizes that the policies, practices and procedures of our company ensure consistent \r\n\r\nquality in the product and services that we provide our clients.</span> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\'text-align:justify\'><span lang=EN style=\'color:navy\'><span\r\nlang=EN style=\'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\";color:navy;\r\nfont-weight:normal\'>We believe that our decision to become ISO 9001:2008 Certified is a proactive one that not only anticipates the demands of our clients, \r\n\r\nbut also demonstrates our commitment for providing quality software services to all our clients.  We look forward to your continuing support in helping us \r\n\r\nsustain this standard and progress towards achieving further quality standards in the years to come.</span> </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:.5in\'><span style=\'font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Book Antiqua\";color:navy\'>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-IN style=\'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\";\r\ncolor:navy\'>Warm regards,</span></p>\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-IN style=\'font-size:8.0pt;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\";\r\ncolor:navy\'>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-IN style=\'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\";\r\ncolor:navy\'>#FROMNAME#.</span></p>\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-IN style=\'font-size:8.0pt;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\";\r\ncolor:navy\'>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoAutoSig style=\'margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt\'><strong><span\r\nlang=EN style=\'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\";color:navy;\r\nfont-weight:normal\'>This email and its attachments may be confidential and are\r\nintended solely for the use of the individual / department / organization to\r\nwhom it is addressed. If you are not the intended recipient of this email and\r\nits attachments, you must take no action based upon them, nor must you copy or\r\nshow them to anyone. Please contact tech@gnsaindia.com if you believe you\r\nhave received this email in error. It is also confirmed that this mail has been\r\nscanned by McAfee VirusScan Enterprise version 8.7i for malicious software. </span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span lang=EN style=\'color:navy\'>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><strong><span lang=EN\r\nstyle=\'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\";color:navy;font-weight:normal\'>GNSA\r\nInfotech Ltd, Block E &amp; F, Nelson Chambers, 115 Nelson Manickam Road,\r\nAminjikarai, Chennai - 600 029.</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:.5in\'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>','ISO Certification - Flexicode','Y'),(2,NULL,'<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\"\r\nxmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\"\r\nxmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\"\r\nxmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\r\n\r\n<head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=Content-Type content=\"text/html; charset=windows-1252\">\r\n<meta name=ProgId content=Word.Document>\r\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 1