, <b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'>GNSA\r\nInfotech Ltd (GNSA)</b>. We have been active in the BPO &amp; Share Transfer\r\nAgency space since 1985.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>  </span>We service some\r\nof the largest clients, (MNC Banks, MNCs, Indian Listed companies) PAN India.\r\nOver the years we have built &quot;best industry practices&quot; in our domains\r\nwhich has ensured that we service our clients efficiently.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'>To allow you have a better\r\nperspective, I am attaching a brochure on our Company and services provided. I\r\nhave also attached a separate brochure on our capabilities in the share\r\ntransfer domain. I would urge you to have a look at this document whenever time\r\npermits. We are fully aware that you must be engaged with some other <b\r\nstyle=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'>Share Transfer Agent</b> and you might need\r\ntime to think about our firm. We, sincerely acknowledge your time and efforts\r\nfor reading this mail</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'>In case, you are interested to\r\nknow anything about our company please feel free to contact me at 9600016903 or\r\ncall on me at our address given below.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>  </span>I\r\nam sure we could scale up operations &amp; add value to you thru our share\r\ntransfer agency services. I also welcome you &amp; your team to visit our\r\nfacility anytime. Just give me a call before you do so.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'>Thanks &amp; regards</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'>R Devasahayam</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'>Head - Share Transfer Agency</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'>GNSA Infotech Ltd</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'>Phone: 044 - 42962025</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>','Our Share Transfer Agency Services','Y'),(5,NULL,'<html>\r\n\r\n<head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=Content-Type content=\"text/html; charset=windows-1252\">\r\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 11 (filtered)\">\r\n<title>GNSA Infotech Limited</title>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n<!--\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\r\n	{margin:0in;\r\n	margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Times New Roman\";}\r\n@page Section1\r\n	{size:8.5in 11.0in;\r\n	margin:1.0in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\r\ndiv.Section1\r\n	{page:Section1;}\r\n-->\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n\r\n<body lang=EN-US>\r\n\r\n<div class=Section1>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style=\'text-align:center\'><span\r\nstyle=\'font-size:12.0pt\'>GNSA Infotech Limited</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style=\'text-align:center\'><span\r\nstyle=\'font-size:12.0pt\'>Nelson Chambers, STA Department, F-Block, 4th Floor</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style=\'text-align:center\'><span\r\n  style=\'font-size:12.0pt\'># 115 Nelson Manickam Road</span><span\r\nstyle=\'font-size:12.0pt\'>, Aminjikarai, Chennai – 600 029</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style=\'text-align:center\'><span\r\nstyle=\'font-size:12.0pt\'>Phone: 044-42962025</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt\'>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt\'>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt\'>8th\r\nJune 2013</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt\'>&nbsp;</sp