ond\r\nappropriately to enable us to serve you effectively….</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt\'>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt\'>Thanking\r\nYou.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt\'>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt\'>For\r\nBimetal Bearings Limited                            For GNSA Infotech Limited                                         </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt\'>(Sd.) K.Vidhya Shankar                                   (Sd.) N.Krishnakumar</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt\'>DGM &amp; Company Secretary                            Director</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>','Green Initiative','Y'),(6,NULL,'<html>\r\n\r\n<head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=Content-Type content=\"text/html; charset=windows-1252\">\r\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 11 (filtered)\">\r\n<title> </title>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n<!--\r\n /* Font Definitions */\r\n @font-face\r\n	{font-family:Calibri;}\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:\"Book Antiqua\";\r\n	panose-1:2 4 6 2 5 3 5 3 3 4;}\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:\"Mongolian Baiti\";}\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\r\n	{margin:0in;\r\n	margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	font-size:11.0pt;\r\n	font-family:Calibri;}\r\na:link, span.MsoHyperlink\r\n	{color:blue;\r\n	text-decoration:underline;}\r\na:visited, span.MsoHyperlinkFollowed\r\n	{color:purple;\r\n	text-decoration:underline;}\r\n@page Section1\r\n	{size:595.3pt 841.9pt;\r\n	margin:1.0in 1.0in 1.0in 1.0in;}\r\ndiv.Section1\r\n	{page:Section1;}\r\n-->\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n\r\n<body lang=EN-US link=blue vlink=purple>\